
Valid Number

Validate if a given string is numeric.

Some examples:
"0" => true
" 0.1 " => true
"abc" => false
"1 a" => false
"2e10" => true


There can not be space between numbers.

You can use the point only once and you have to have numbers later.

It can be used only once, it has to have numbers before and after and there can be no point after or just before it.
